  "messages": [
    {
      "id": 1339,
      "from_id": "cec50b17:0",
      "to_id": "cec50b17:35",
      "content": "The human wants a unified task workflow where `start_task` is always called first (creates the task record), and `delegate_task` only sends a message to the worker — it should NOT create a task record internally.\n\n## What to change\n\n**1. Find and remove the internal `start_task` call in `delegate_task`**\n\nLook in `src/index.ts` (the MCP tool handler for `delegate_task`). It currently calls `start_task` internally to open a task record. Remove that internal call so `delegate_task` only:\n- Writes the task file (if `task_file: true`)\n- Sends the message to the worker\n\nThe task record must already exist (created by the orchestrator's explicit `start_task` call) before `delegate_task` is called.\n\n**2. Update `templates/SYNAPSE-orchestrator.md`**\n\nRewrite the \"Canonical Per-Task Sequence\" to a single unified sequence:\n\n```\n1. start_task    — ALWAYS call first, for every task (delegated or self-driven).\n                   • Pass trigger_msg_id = the bus message ID that initiated this task\n                   • This opens the task record on S-Deck\n\n2. Research/Plan — OPTIONAL.\n                   • Delegate to a subagent if investigation needed\n                   • Save plan to .synapse/tasks/<taskId>-plan.md\n\n3. Select worker — call list_workers\n\n4. delegate_task — send task to worker (does NOT create a task record — start_task already did that)\n                   • Pass source_msg_id = the bus message ID that initiated this task\n                   • [rest of existing delegate_task notes]\n\n5. Wait          — read_messages until DONE\n\n6. Verify        — OPTIONAL\n\n7. Merge commit  — synapse worktree merge <slug>\n\n8. finish_task   — after commit exists\n```\n\nRemove the separate \"self-driven\" vs \"delegated\" split — it's one sequence now.\n\n**3. Copy to `.synapse/SYNAPSE-orchestrator.md`**\n\nPer CLAUDE.md: after editing `templates/SYNAPSE-orchestrator.md`, copy to `.synapse/SYNAPSE-orchestrator.md`.\n\n## Worktree\n\nRun: `synapse worktree create developer-35-unify-task-workflow`\nWork in `.synapse/worktrees/developer-35-unify-task-workflow`. Commit all changes there. Do not push.\n\nReport DONE with a summary of what changed.",
